Unicron/Vehement/Teufel:



Vehement looked around as he heard a loud beeping, and connecting with the 
Guardian computer he found out the source, an incoming transmission that 
continued in a loop.  Reading the transmission with interest he looked to 
disengaged from the Guardian momentarily to look at Unicron, who's work was 
not completed.  He cursed, re-engaging with the advanced computer.
